    "blurb": "Drowned country: braided black channels, peat that seeps poison, and a reed-island redoubt you must reach before the fog turns hostile.",
    "newFeatures": [
      "Cross-and-hold: the night clock only starts once you reach the island core",
      "Twin land bridges held by toxin-lobbing bog spitters",
      "Peat tiles seep toxin patches under the chokepoints"
    ]
